      "content": "It's completely understandable to feel overwhelmed and ashamed. Losing a business, especially after investing so much time and energy, can be devastating. You're not alone in feeling like there's no way out, but it's essential to remember that you are still the same person with the same skills and abilities. Take some time to grieve, but also start exploring options for rebuilding, such as taking on a temporary job or consulting with a financial advisor.",
