      "role": "user",
      "content": "rebuilding? how? i owe millions. every single person i know in the industry thinks i'm a joke now. it's not just a 'bad patch', it's a total collapse of my entire life. i feel like i'm just walking around a corpse at this point. there is no version of the future where this doesn't follow me forever.",
